snippet: Just eighteen days after the end of the men’s golf season, it started again at the Frys.com Open at CordeValle Golf Club, which had more tour members than spots available.
abstract: Men’s PGA Tour starts again at the Frys.com Open at CordeValle Golf Club, just eighteen days after the season-ending Tour Championship.
lead_paragraph: Just eighteen days after the end of the men’s golf season, it started again at the Frys.com Open at CordeValle Golf Club, which had more tour members than spots available.

headline.main: Not Wasting Time, PGA Starts New Season With a Crowd
headline.print_headline: Not Wasting Time, PGA Starts New Season With a Crowd
